00:01:49.330 --> 00:01:51.390
I remember one day I found the face brick,

00:01:51.390 --> 00:01:55.190
and you know I got the, all the
kids were like (car noises).

00:01:55.190 --> 00:01:57.627
And I've got the little
swag, and they're like,

00:01:57.627 --> 00:01:59.310
"Oh Trevor, are you
playing, are you playing?"

00:01:59.310 --> 00:02:00.380
And then I was like, "Yeah."

00:02:00.380 --> 00:02:02.720
