out from behind my back.

00:02:02.720 --> 00:02:05.570
And they're like (gasps)
"Face brick, face brick."

00:02:05.570 --> 00:02:07.547
And it's like, "Now he has
a face brick, face brick."

00:02:07.547 --> 00:02:08.730
And it's like, "Let's go."

00:02:08.730 --> 00:02:10.480
