00:02:27.731 --> 00:02:28.650
It's like a big thing.

00:02:28.650 --> 00:02:30.450
And then you'd play, and
you'd take the brick,

00:02:30.450 --> 00:02:32.290
and it was such a popular thing

00:02:32.290 --> 00:02:35.140
