if you lived in the townships

00:02:35.140 --> 00:02:37.300
because kids would steal
bricks from outside your house

00:02:37.300 --> 00:02:39.110
if you were doing renovations,

00:02:39.110 --> 00:02:40.300
so if you weren't careful,

00:02:40.300 --> 00:02:41.810
