00:02:54.727 --> 00:02:57.190
"I don't know what you're
talking about, man.

00:02:57.190 --> 00:02:59.120
This is my favorite toy."

00:02:59.120 --> 00:03:01.040
It just makes you realize,
you can just have fun

00:03:01.040 --> 00:03:03.990
with anything, man, it was,
that was genuinely my favorite.

00:03:03.990 --> 00:03:06.760
Even now when I see bricks, I get happy.

00:03:06.760 --> 00:03:08.030
Like I said to friends,

00:03:08.030 --> 00:03:09.830
that's the one thing I
don't like about living

00:03:09.830 --> 00:03:12.140
