00:03:14.730 --> 00:03:16.617
You take that for granted,
I walk around, I'm like,

00:03:16.617 --> 00:03:19.220
"Man, no bricks, no bricks,
no bricks, no bricks."

00:03:19.220 --> 00:03:21.320
And if I see a brick,
there's a thing in me still

00:03:21.320 --> 00:03:23.270
