00:04:21.803 --> 00:04:23.430
He's like, "We gotta go get water."

00:04:23.430 --> 00:04:24.387
And I'm like, "What?"

00:04:24.387 --> 00:04:26.070
And then you get the wheelbarrow,

00:04:26.070 --> 00:04:27.700
