00:05:22.380 --> 00:05:24.710
and I'm joking obviously,
I'm being facetious.

00:05:24.710 --> 00:05:26.350
No, I had no clue.

00:05:26.350 --> 00:05:28.319
Nor did I wish for that,
I'll be honest with you.

00:05:28.319 --> 00:05:31.330
I was, I still joke with my
mom about that 'til this day.

00:05:31.330 --> 00:05:33.110
I go, "I did not know
where life would take me,

00:05:33.110 --> 00:05:34.570
or how life would end up.

00:05:34.570 --> 00:05:37.500
All I knew is that I
wanted to be able to afford

00:05:37.500 --> 00:05:40.520
to buy as much food as I wanted to buy.

00:05:40.520 --> 00:05:41.500
Like at any time."

00:05:41.500 --> 00:05:43.623
That was the big time in my life.

00:05:43.623 --> 00:05:46.564
'Cause when you don't
have money in a family,

00:05:46.564 --> 00:05:49.805
