00:18:20.210 --> 00:18:22.309
but the police in the country were afraid

00:18:22.309 --> 00:18:24.530
of Winnie Mandela, you know, they were.

00:18:24.530 --> 00:18:26.810
And we had a phrase in
South Africa that was,

00:18:26.810 --> 00:18:28.034
we still use it today, which was

00:18:28.034 --> 00:18:30.530
"Wathint' abafazi, wathint' imbokodo'"

00:18:30.530 --> 00:18:33.440
which means, "You strike a
woman you strike a rock."

00:18:33.440 --> 00:18:34.273
And that's what

00:18:34.273 --> 00:18:36.231
I grew up learning.
