00:18:36.231 --> 00:18:38.640
That was, it was kudos, man.

00:18:40.343 --> 00:18:41.593
It was fire, it was fire.

00:18:42.700 --> 00:18:45.374
And a lot of the time, my mom
would strike me with a rock.

